Patch summary:
Refresh x86_64 and arm64 libvulkan NDK ABI dumps for Vulkan-Headers v1.4.341.

The local Vulkan-Headers pin exposes the newer 1.4.341 enum surface through
x86_64 and arm64 libvulkan for every finalized NDK API level that libvulkan
exports (API 24 through API 36). Keep the checked-in NDK ABI reference dumps
in sync with freshly generated stg dumps so stgdiff accepts the desktop
x86_64 and arm64 builds. All changes are enum-only additions; no interfaces
are removed or modified.

